_Bool can_find_free_mob ( void  )

Find a free MOB.

Returns:
True if an empty MOB has been found, false if all MOB are in use.

This function scan all 15 MOB starting from MOB 0 to MOB 14 (highest priority first) and set MOB page to either the first empty MOB encounter or to MOB 14.
